<div class="container">
  <form action="/demo_generator" method="post" class="form-vertical">
    <input type="hidden" name="task_input" id="task_input" value=""/>
    <fieldset>
      <h3>Tasks Generator Helper for analyzing an area</h3>

      <p>This is a (demo) helper to generate crowdmapping tasks. This helper will cut an area into an overlapping grid of smaller
        areas according to a given resolution. The result will be a google fusion table ready to be used as input for
        MicroTask.(next step: create your own instructions / task interpreter to process them) </p>

      <hr/>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="span12">
          <h2> Fusion table generated !</h2>
          <p>Table ID (to copy) <br/><h4 class="alert alert-info"><%= @table_id %></h4>
          </p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="http://www.google.com/fusiontables/DataSource?docid=<%= @table_id %>">See
            the generated tasks</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr/>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="span12">
          <h2> Next step</h2>
          <p>Create your own task interpreter to process these tasks
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="/apps/new?input_ft=<%= @table_id %>">Create app</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
</div>